  "instructions": "Welcome to the hardest part of English! Some action words do NOT accept the '-ed' ending. If you say 'Eated', people will not understand you. You must memorize these 15 'Rule Breaker' words. You have to learn them like completely new words.",
  "contentItems": [
    {
      "type": "note",
      "text": "For example: The past of THINK is THOUGHT. There is no simple trick to guess it. You just have to practice!"
    }
  ],
